Sdcard remapper (Xposed)

Use example file Noremap.txt and place it to /storage/sdcard0

Description:
logging:true - Enable logging to Xposed error.log (with prefix 'Remap: ').
package:com.speedsoftware.rootexplorer - Disable remap for package with name 'com.speedsoftware.rootexplorer'.
package:com.mediatek.filemanager - Disable remap for package with name 'com.mediatek.filemanager'.
Android - Let app to skip remap files with path starts with /storage/sdcard0/Android or /sdcard/Android.
DCIM - Let app to skip remap files with path starts with /storage/sdcard0/DCIM or /sdcard/DCIM.
and the same lines for other directories.